sequenceDiagram
    participant Bank
    participant DALP
    participant SmartContract
    participant Investor
    participant Custody

    Bank->>DALP: Configure deposit token
    DALP->>SmartContract: Deploy token contract
    Investor->>DALP: KYC + onboarding
    DALP->>SmartContract: Whitelist investor
    Bank->>DALP: Initiate mint
    DALP->>SmartContract: Mint deposit tokens
    SmartContract->>Investor: Tokens credited
    Investor->>DALP: Request redemption
    DALP->>SmartContract: Burn tokens
    SmartContract->>Custody: Release underlying
    Custody->>Investor: Settlement complete
